Job Posting Title:   SE_Real Estate SME_Senior
Description:   1.1.2 Handläggande Arkitekt

Real Estate SME drive and lead development and implementation of the design, maintenance, construction and renovation of manufacturing and non-manufacturing property (buildings, equipment and other facilities). They guide and support in one or more of the specific areas below:
- Property Management (e.g., property management, technical requirements, waste disposal etc.)
- Workplace experience
- Property Planning (e.g., space planning, facility infrastructure condition assessment, etc.)
- Property Security
- Planning maintenance programs for building and grounds.

Real Estate SME on Senior level applies advanced knowledge typically obtained through education and work experience. Responsibilities may include:
- Managing projects / processes, working independently with limited supervision.
- Coaching and reviewing the work of lower level professionals.
- Problems faced are difficult and sometimes complex.

Senior: position typically requires >5 years relevant experience

Volvo Group is an equal opportunity employer that values diversity in our workplace and we welcome all applicants regardless of age, ethnicity, gender or cultural background.

Job Posting Start Date:   2024-01-12
Job Posting End Date:   2024-06-30
Location:   Skövde
Job Family:   Real Estate
Price: 801 sek/h

